value.0: A portal glows softly before you. You wonder where it leads.

We consecrate this shrine to our lady Serena as a place of life and healing in this foul domain.  We swear on our devotion to Serena to strive our utmost to rid our world of the foul beast within that seeks to corrupt all that our lady stands for.
A small altar rests before you. You catch your reflection in its polished gleam, feeling somehow at peace within its presence.
The water tumbles into the pool below, the sound of its fall marking a cheerful note.
Specially blessed by Serena, this water has damaging effects against the Undead.
